&lt;li&gt;Develop cost models to effectively capture the true cost of client’s products or services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify the inefficiencies within processes tied to the office of the CFO and recommend opportunities for automation or improvement. Processes include but are not limited to:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AR/AP Processing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Month End Close&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Financial Reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Job/Product Costing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Budgeting/Forecasting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support client pricing strategy conversations based on market comfort, cost modeling, margin expectations, and strategic business goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automate the completion of monthly/quarterly/yearly financial reporting for clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, develop, and deliver training to the client as needed to ensure proper change management of initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with project team to define project requirements by identifying project milestones, phases, and deliverables&lt;/li&gt;
